<template>
  <template>
    <v-data-table
        v-model="selected"
        :headers="headers"
        :items="desserts"
        :single-select="singleSelect"
        item-key="name"
        show-select
        class="elevation-1"
    >
      <template v-slot:top>
        <v-switch
            v-model="singleSelect"
            label="Single select"
            class="pa-3"
        ></v-switch>
      </template>
    </v-data-table>
  </template>
</template>

<script>
import {reactive} from "vue";

export default {
  name: "adminManageUsers",
  setup() {
    let headers = reactive([
      {
        text: 'Dessert (100g serving)',
        align: 'start',
        sortable: false,
        value: 'name',
      },
      { text: 'Calories', value: 'calories' },
      { text: 'Fat (g)', value: 'fat' },
      { text: 'Carbs (g)', value: 'carbs' },
      { text: 'Protein (g)', value: 'protein' },
      { text: 'Iron (%)', value: 'iron' },
    ])
    return {
      headers
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
